snippet.title: Lufia and the Fortress of Doom Intro
snippet.description:
I cannot believe that this intro isn't up on youtube already!  Anyway, here is the intro to one of my favorite SNES games, Lufia and the Fortress of Doom.  The music is epic!

Edit: Well, I found out that someone did have the intro movie on youtube, but its from the original Japanese version.  So I guess now you have a choice.
